(2, 102, 'customer', 'Beacon Diagnostics Pvt. Ltd. is a Reagent manufacturing and marketing company. It was established in 1990 and has been successfully manufacturing and marketing it products for more than 25 years in India and some countries abroad.<br />\n<br />\nBeacon is an ISO 9001:2015 and ISO 13485:2003 certified company having its plants and office at Navsari, Gujarat. It is CE certified.<br />\n<br />\nBeacon is engaged in manufacturing of Serology products and Biochemistry reagents. Its Serology manufacturing includes Widal test, RPR, PPD and ASO, CRP, RF latex tests. It manufactures wide range of routine and specialized biochemistry test reagents and System Packs. All manufacturing is done at its sophisticated manufacturing facility in an area covering more than 40,000 sq ft, at Navsari, Gujarat, INDIA. It has more than 100 employees at its plant and head office for various activities of management, manufacturing, Quality control and R&D, administration and logistic support.<br />\n<br />\nBeacon has pan India operation with more than 100 field staff, including 15 Application specialists to promote its products to customers. It engages more than 250 Distributors to support its customer all over India.<br />\n<br />\nBeacon has international sales and distribution network supplying in many Asian, African & European countries. Over the years Beacon has globalize with leading international companies to build up a comprehensive product range & services for its customers.<br />\n<br />\nIn India, It cover all majors customers including Private market, Semi Government sectors like NACO, Railways, Armed forces and other major Public sectors and all major Government sectors like Civil hospitals, Primary health centers.<br />\n<br />\nBeacon sincerely believes to employ genius and talented people, adopt new technologies to develop products and to continuously improve product quality and services .', NULL, 1, '2020-05-31 16:45:21'),
